posting_body: ['2 - 3 Bedroom  2 - 2.5 Bathroom | 1244 - 1492 sq ft | $1170 - $1332/Month', 'Columbia Wood', '166 Greison Trl', 'Newnan, GA 30263', 'show contact info', 'Description:', 'Affordable Housing - Income Restrictions Apply!', 'Looking for an apartment for rent in Newnan, GA?', 'Tour one of our townhomes today!Welcome home to a comfortable community with beautiful townhomes for rent in Newnan, GA.', "At Columbia Wood, we're excited to offer quality two- and three-bedroom floor plans.", "Take advantage of large closet space and air conditioning - but that's not all!", 'Some of our community amenities include easy access to public transportation, an on-site fitness center, and a swimming pool.', "Curious about what's nearby the community?", "Within minutes of leaving Columbia Wood, you'll find great restaurants like Knife and Stone and Fabiano's Pizzeria of Newnan.", "You're also never too far away from great shopping and entertainment venues.", 'Apartment Amenities:', '➢ Air Conditioner', '➢ Carpeting', '➢ Ceiling Fan', '➢ Dishwasher', '➢ Disposal', '➢ Large Closets', '➢ W/D Hookup', '➢ Window Coverings', 'Our Residents Enjoy:', '➢ Clubhouse', '➢ Fitness Center', '➢ Playground', '➢ Pool', '➢ Business Center', '➢ On-Site Maintenance', '➢ Public Transportation', 'Additional Details:', 'Deposit: Call', 'Terms: 12-Month', 'Pets: No pets allowed.', 'Service animals allowed.', 'Please see the office for more details.', 'show contact info', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY']
